1411.name: OA S-70-T4R
1411.Applications: Welding outside in case high speed welding is required and protective gas is not possible or difficult. Suitable for C-Mn steels such as rails, fabrication of machinery, steel framed buildings and or heavy equipment repair. Recommended for butt assembly of rails and crossings.
1411.Suitable_For: Rebuilding and joining steel parts that requires good strenght and high productivity.
